 $40 and the closest garage had a sign for $30 a day. In the end it was a good stay, but if I could go back (because San Francisco was an amazing city!) I would stay closer in towards the heart of the city for that price and probably picked something myself rather than a travel agent who didn't get us any sort of deal.	
