Aug 18 2005	Nice Hotel that is Not the Holiday Inn	Some folks have posted their opinions of what I think may be the Holiday Inn. The Holiday Inn Express is directly next door to a building that is part of the Holiday Inn, but they are NOT the same hotel. The HI Express has 4 floors, not 5 and no pool. This was my second stay and it was just as nice as the first. Our room was very clean and the free breakfast was ample--unlike some other places they quickly replenish items if they start running out. We stayed in a minisuite facing Beach St. and it was very quiet--we could even see Alcatraz from our room. the hotel is safe, nicely decorated and clean. You can't beat the location if you want to be on Fisherman's Wharf. There are lots of public transportation options nearby and you can easily walk to North Beach or to Ghirardelli Square. Overall this is a good value particularly for the area. In the past I've found that the front desk staff can be somewhat unpleasant but did not have any issues with them this time. Actually the front desk clerk called a limousine for us to take to the airport--we had a private car with plenty of room for less than the cost of a taxi.	
Aug 17 2005	Great Location	Stayed here for 3 nights at the end of our family trip to the USA - 2 adults &amp; 2 children.Location wise the hotel is great. Check in staff were very helpful and friendly. Room was clean and tidy, not huge but big enough for the four of us. On site parking, because we were with Virgin, was free (and very secure).Had read about the noise at night outside being an issue from other posts on here, but have to say we had no problems whatsoever.Two minutes from the hotel is the old 1940's tram system which will take you for a $1.25 fare all the way to downtown and back. Alternatively the cable car stop is also a couple of minutes away. Fisherman's Wharf itself is a little overrated, but the city has so many other things to see and do, that it is as good a base as anywhere to stay.Would I stay at the hotel again?...... Yes as it's safe, secure and in a good location	
